330
00:27:09,488 --> 00:27:11,688
Who didn't think the church and science were enemies...

331
00:27:11,900 --> 00:27:14,130
but just a different language telling the same story.

332
00:27:14,323 --> 00:27:15,885
Anyone of like minds could find the
Church of Illumintation.

333
00:27:16,120 --> 00:27:20,381
But he couldn't exactly advertise its location so
