00:27:28,037 --> 00:27:31,568
Then some unknown Illuminati master sculpted four statues.

337
00:27:31,918 --> 00:27:34,403
Each one a tribute to
one of the fundamental elements:

338
00:27:34,602 --> 00:27:36,977
earth, air, fire, water.

