Where are we going?
- To see my father.

716
01:03:48,121 --> 01:03:49,602
I don't understand.

717
01:03:49,626 --> 01:03:52,422
I was orphaned when I was nine years of age.

718
01:03:52,587 --> 01:03:57,053
A bombing in Ulster, the UVF protesting
the visit of a Catholic Archbishop.

719
01:03:57,133 --> 01:04:01,377
The Archbishop felt responsible
and he adopted me the following day.

720
01:04:01,638 --> 01:04:04,184
I was raised by him and by the Church.

721
01:04:04,754 --> 01:04:07,107
He was the wisest man I ever met.

722
01:04:07,568 --> 01:04:11,265
Even when I was young and stubborn,
I wanted to be ordained...

723
01:04:11,300 --> 01:04:14,741
but I was brought up in Italy, so
I also wanted to do my military service.

724
01:04:14,746 --> 01:04:16,678
I wanted to fight.

725
01:04:17,115 --> 01:04:20,105
He told me, "Learn to fly."

726
01:04:20,138 --> 01:04:24,007
So, I joined the Aeronautica Militare.
Flew helicopters.

727
01:04:24,017 --> 01:04:26,419
Bringing the wounded
back to hospitals.

728
01:04:26,424 --> 01:04:29,514
He was a great man.
- Your father died.

729
01:04:30,379 --> 01:04:32,057
Fourteen days ago.

730
01:04:33,249 --> 01:04:35,144
Headquarters, you hear me?

731
01:04:35,382 --> 01:04:38,112
The flow is completed.
Oxygen level is very low.

732
01:04:38,113 --> 01:04:41,615
Answer, please.
- Did you get anything?

733
01:04:41,623 --> 01:04:45,304
No. The walls are lead lined. There's no signal.

734
01:07:59,735 --> 01:08:00,740
This way.

735
01:08:08,646 --> 01:08:12,626
If the Holy Father was murdered,
the implications are profound.

736
01:08:12,645 --> 01:08:14,954
Vatican security is impenetrable.

737
01:08:14,961 --> 01:08:17,503
No one from the outside
could've got anywhere near him.

738
01:08:17,876 --> 01:08:21,592
It was someone on the inside.
- Then we can trust no one.

739
01:08:23,572 --> 01:08:27,518
On my screen, no response
in zone 7.

740
01:08:27,557 --> 01:08:31,539
With all these power cuts,
the battery will soon be empty...

741
01:08:31,758 --> 01:08:34,021
the device will explode at midnight.

742
01:08:55,651 --> 01:08:57,223
Holy Father...

743
01:08:58,163 --> 01:09:02,209
when I was young, you told me
the voice in my heart was God's voice.

744
01:09:02,244 --> 01:09:05,667
You said I should follow
it no matter how painful.

745
01:09:05,674 --> 01:09:07,034
Forgive me.

746
01:09:08,744 --> 01:09:10,369
Please, give me strength.

747
01:09:11,554 --> 01:09:16,165
What I do, I do in the
name of everything you believe.

748
01:10:06,452 --> 01:10:08,287
God help us.

749
01:10:20,754 --> 01:10:23,521
Santa Maria della Vittoria.
Do you know it?

750
01:10:23,994 --> 01:10:26,407
Yes, I do.
- It's the next church.

751
01:10:42,667 --> 01:10:44,521
I think someone just tried to kill me.

752
01:10:44,529 --> 01:10:47,707
Professor, I promise you, we had no idea.
- He knows I'm here?

753
01:10:47,713 --> 01:10:49,837
- Yes.
- You heard me ask permission.
You gave me an escort.

754
01:10:49,842 --> 01:10:54,154
Yes, but we had no idea that portions
of our white zones were crosswired with that building.

755
01:10:55,148 --> 01:10:56,941
Commander Richter was extending the search.

756
01:10:56,943 --> 01:11:00,165
If he had known the archives
were on that grid, he never would
have killed the power.

757
01:11:01,227 --> 01:11:03,287
But there is the other possibility.

758
01:11:03,471 --> 01:11:06,372
Is it conceivable the Illuminati...

759
01:11:06,919 --> 01:11:09,403
have infiltrated the Swiss Guard?

760
01:11:12,046 --> 01:11:13,454
Perhaps.

761
01:11:23,592 --> 01:11:25,439
The journals. Where are they?

762
01:11:28,042 --> 01:11:30,367
Who took the journals from this desk?

763
01:11:40,392 --> 01:11:43,195
Signore, this is unacceptable.

764
01:11:43,692 --> 01:11:46,772
For a Camerlengo to enter the chapel
once conclave has begun.

765
01:11:46,779 --> 01:11:47,856
Forgive me.

766
01:11:47,857 --> 01:11:49,679
There's been a development.

767
01:12:00,237 --> 01:12:06,850
His Holiness Celestine was murdered!
- Is it so inconceivable that it will happen again?

768
01:12:06,852 --> 01:12:09,753
Signori, please, a moment. Please. Signori.

769
01:12:12,223 --> 01:12:14,667
Our church is at war.

770
01:12:15,740 --> 01:12:18,986
We are under attack from an old enemy.

771
01:12:19,345 --> 01:12:21,170
The Illuminati.

772
01:12:21,666 --> 01:12:24,186
They have struck us from within.

773
01:12:24,190 --> 01:12:26,386
Murdering our Holy Father!

774
01:12:26,421 --> 01:12:30,948
And threatening us all with destruction at
the hands of their new God 'Science'.

775
01:12:31,062 --> 01:12:34,309
They call it retribution.
They think it justified...

776
01:12:34,344 --> 01:12:38,491
because of the Church's attacks
on men of science in the distant past
and it's true.

777
01:12:39,199 --> 01:12:44,264
Since the days of Galileo,
this church has tried to slow
the relentless march of progress.

778
01:12:44,299 --> 01:12:46,533
Sometimes with misguided means.

779
01:12:48,042 --> 01:12:50,134
But science and religion
are not enemies.

780
01:12:51,750 --> 01:12:56,420
There are simply some things that
science is just too young to understand.

781
01:12:56,750 --> 01:12:58,596
So the Church pleads, "Stop."

782
01:12:59,130 --> 01:13:00,391
"Slow down."

783
01:13:00,573 --> 01:13:01,921
"Think. Wait."

784
01:13:02,100 --> 01:13:03,965
And, for this, they call us backwards.

785
01:13:05,084 --> 01:13:06,844
But who is more ignorant?

786
01:13:07,174 --> 01:13:09,178
The man who cannot define lightning...

787
01:13:09,541 --> 01:13:12,650
or the man who does not respect
its natural awesome power?

788
01:13:13,739 --> 01:13:15,885
The battle is well under way, signori.

789
01:13:16,619 --> 01:13:18,550
We must defend ourselves.

790
01:13:18,758 --> 01:13:21,327
But, what if this time, we fight
their stealth with openness?

791
01:13:21,502 --> 01:13:24,189
Combat their wicked scheme with simple truth.

792
01:13:24,382 --> 01:13:27,333
And end this brutish battle once and for all.

793
01:13:27,528 --> 01:13:30,342
If the outside world could see
this church as I do...

794
01:13:30,546 --> 01:13:32,441
looking beyond the
ritual of these walls...

795
01:13:32,638 --> 01:13:35,172
they would see a modern miracle.

796
01:13:35,382 --> 01:13:38,953
A brotherhood of
imperfect, simple souls...

797
01:13:39,148 --> 01:13:43,994
who want nothing more than to be
voices of compassion in a world
spinning out of control.

798
01:13:46,249 --> 01:13:48,676
Signori, I ask..

799
01:13:49,911 --> 01:13:51,640
I pray...

800
01:13:52,879 --> 01:13:55,161
that you break this conclave.

801
01:13:55,473 --> 01:13:56,829
Open the doors...

802
01:13:57,979 --> 01:13:59,708
evacuate St. Peter's Square...

803
01:14:00,310 --> 01:14:02,004
and tell the world the truth.

804
01:14:37,532 --> 01:14:39,136
Get him down.

805
01:14:50,817 --> 01:14:53,289
There. There, that chain. On that pulley.

806
01:14:53,509 --> 01:14:54,908
This bench. Get this pew off here and
make it a ladder.

807
01:16:16,929 --> 01:16:18,329
Vatican Police.

808
01:17:20,364 --> 01:17:23,095
My son...

809
01:17:23,130 --> 01:17:26,571
God answers all prayers, but...

810
01:17:27,373 --> 01:17:29,764
sometimes His answer is no.

811
01:17:30,937 --> 01:17:33,625
The College will not break conclave.

812
01:17:34,762 --> 01:17:36,739
May I suggest...

813
01:17:37,138 --> 01:17:42,351
you direct your energies to helping the
Swiss Guard find this explosive device.

814
01:17:42,356 --> 01:17:44,028
If it exists.

815
01:17:45,208 --> 01:17:47,933
And leave Church leadership...

816
01:17:49,659 --> 01:17:51,482
to its leaders.

817
01:18:03,562 --> 01:18:04,792
Eminence.

818
01:18:07,054 --> 01:18:09,331
There is a growing fear...

819
01:18:10,023 --> 01:18:12,180
that without the four Preferiti...

820
01:18:12,185 --> 01:18:17,164
it defers much authority for any candidate.
It will not be possible...

821
01:18:17,479 --> 01:18:19,650
Unless...
- Speak plainly.

822
01:18:20,918 --> 01:18:24,649
It is the recommendation of many
that you asked to be removed...

823
01:18:24,655 --> 01:18:26,897
from your post as Great Elector.

824
01:18:27,172 --> 01:18:33,584
Thereby making yourself
eligible to wear the Ring of the Fisherman.

825
01:18:36,392 --> 01:18:38,652
Well, if it is God's will.

826
01:18:45,727 --> 01:18:47,725
May His will be done.

827
01:19:00,522 --> 01:19:02,443
Here! I hear someone.

828
01:19:04,723 --> 01:19:06,355
Remove the lid.

829
01:19:09,111 --> 01:19:10,165
Come on.

830
01:19:14,528 --> 01:19:16,119
Signore, are you okay?

831
01:19:24,423 --> 01:19:26,346
I know he is there.

832
01:19:26,358 --> 01:19:29,401
Madam, it is necessary that you
remain quiet.

833
01:19:29,417 --> 01:19:33,191
Tell me that I should remain calm.
I want to know what he will do.

834
01:19:37,740 --> 01:19:39,589
Commander, here's Ms. Vetra.

835
01:19:41,067 --> 01:19:43,612
Those journals are private property.
I demand that you return them to me.

836
01:19:43,614 --> 01:19:46,751
They're material evidence in
a Vatican investigation.

837
01:19:49,052 --> 01:19:52,967
I am an Italian citizen.
My rights do not end just
because I crossed the other side.

838
01:19:52,968 --> 01:19:56,194
This is not Italy.
It's not even Rome. It's the Vatican.

839
01:19:56,219 --> 01:19:58,255
A country with its own laws.

840
01:19:58,259 --> 01:20:01,702
And when those journals passed the border,
they became my property.

841
01:20:01,707 --> 01:20:03,431
I will give them back to you...

842
01:20:03,857 --> 01:20:06,888
when I've decided they contain
nothing of value to the investigation.

843
01:20:06,891 --> 01:20:09,227
Do you have something to hide,
Commandante Richter?

844
01:20:12,152 --> 01:20:14,090
Do you, Dr. Vetra?

845
01:20:35,716 --> 01:20:38,070
If it were up to me,
it wouldn't be this way.

846
01:20:39,718 --> 01:20:42,274
It's a sin to kill with pain.

847
01:20:43,524 --> 01:20:45,674
It's a sin to kill without reason, Father.

848
01:20:51,963 --> 01:20:53,325
They made me a sinner.

849
01:21:13,077 --> 01:21:14,749
Saint Theresa on fire.

850
01:21:18,144 --> 01:21:19,125
Professor Langdon?

851
01:21:20,743 --> 01:21:22,895
What direction is that?
- West, I think.

852
01:21:23,090 --> 01:21:24,905
"Across Rome the mystic elements unfold."

853
01:21:27,048 --> 01:21:31,829
Piazza Barba Rini is here.
Saint Theresa is here.

854
01:21:32,744 --> 01:21:34,861
Where is the Santa Maria del Popolo,
the first altar of science?

855
01:21:35,069 --> 01:21:36,285
Santa Maria del Popolo?
- Yes.

856
01:21:38,502 --> 01:21:39,664
Thank you.

857
01:21:40,539 --> 01:21:41,935
St. Peter's is here.

858
01:21:42,801 --> 01:21:44,274
We are here.

859
01:21:46,343 --> 01:21:47,948
A church with water.

860
01:21:50,000 --> 01:21:51,201
Wait. Wait, wait.

861
01:21:52,017 --> 01:21:53,395
Across Rome.

862
01:21:55,531 --> 01:21:57,838
The poem must mean it literally
across Rome.

863
01:21:58,065 --> 01:22:01,377
Professor Langdon. Commander Richter
has ordered me to escort you to the
Vatican immediately.

864
01:22:01,609 --> 01:22:06,169
Piazza Navona.
Earth. Air. Fire. Water.

865
01:22:06,603 --> 01:22:08,342
"A Cross Rome. "

866
01:22:08,895 --> 01:22:10,452
Bernini's Four Rivers.

867
01:22:12,091 --> 01:22:15,041
Professor Langdon, the Vatican
insists that I have to take you
back immediately.

868
01:22:15,258 --> 01:22:17,501
The Vatican is about to
see its fourth cardinal murdered tonight.

869
01:22:17,705 --> 01:22:18,811
Now, look.

870
01:22:19,614 --> 01:22:22,439
You can do as they say
and force me back to the Vatican...

871
01:22:22,752 --> 01:22:25,033
where we can all
mourn his death together.

872
01:22:25,230 --> 01:22:27,297
Or you can show me how
real cops act...

873
01:22:27,527 --> 01:22:30,820
and take me to Piazza Navona,
where we still might be able to stop it.

874
01:22:34,536 --> 01:22:36,493
Oh. By all means, let's talk it over.

875
01:22:37,732 --> 01:22:39,425
In fourteen minutes, he's going
to be dead.

876
01:22:45,239 --> 01:22:46,778
Okay. This way, Professor.

877
01:22:55,488 --> 01:22:56,725
Yes, Padre?

878
01:22:57,135 --> 01:22:59,918
At 11:15, if the church is still
in peril...

879
01:23:01,056 --> 01:23:03,157
give the order to evacuate
the cardinals.

880
01:23:04,270 --> 01:23:05,691
But with dignity.

881
01:23:06,505 --> 01:23:09,407
Let them walk out into St. Peter's
Square with their heads held high.

882
01:23:10,371 --> 01:23:14,600
We don't want the last image of this
church to be of frightened old men
sneaking out the back door.

883
01:23:31,504 --> 01:23:32,834
"Where the angels guide thee..."

884
01:23:38,659 --> 01:23:40,452
There it is. There it is.

885
01:23:40,512 --> 01:23:43,080
Professor, I know this fountain.
There is no angel...

886
01:23:43,286 --> 01:23:45,546
The dove. The angel of peace.

887
01:23:46,127 --> 01:23:47,720
And it's looking in what direction?

888
01:23:48,477 --> 01:23:49,719
Uh...east, I think.

889
01:24:00,908 --> 01:24:03,813
Professor, just wait here.
Stay put.

890
01:24:39,900 --> 01:24:41,539
Good evening. Can you help me?

891
01:24:42,546 --> 01:24:44,366
I'm waiting for a doctor.

892
01:25:00,056 --> 01:25:01,234
Come here.

893
01:25:04,328 --> 01:25:05,425
Calm down. Don't shoot.

894
01:25:42,364 --> 01:25:44,324
Hey!

895
01:25:58,035 --> 01:26:00,184
Help! Somebody help!

896
01:26:38,075 --> 01:26:39,381
Help! Somebody!

897
01:27:50,938 --> 01:27:51,923
Cardinal Baja.

898
01:27:52,921 --> 01:27:53,852
Cardinal Baja.

899
01:27:54,518 --> 01:27:55,544
Si?

900
01:27:55,726 --> 01:27:57,372
Where was he hiding you?

901
01:27:58,370 --> 01:28:00,139
The Church of Illumination. Where is it?

902
01:28:01,684 --> 01:28:03,942
Castel Sant'Angelo.

903
01:28:05,494 --> 01:28:07,295
Castle of the Angel.

904
01:28:28,743 --> 01:28:30,918
Sir, there's news about Cardinal Baja.

905
01:28:32,155 --> 01:28:35,016
The cardinal told Langdon he was
being held in Castel Sant'Angelo.

906
01:28:35,794 --> 01:28:37,844
If Langdon's right,
that's where the bomb is.

907
01:28:38,621 --> 01:28:41,072
Send everyone we can spare.
- And you?

908
01:28:41,622 --> 01:28:42,676
I'm staying here.

909
01:28:55,847 --> 01:28:56,901
Vittoria.

910
01:28:58,265 --> 01:29:00,090
You're all right?
- I'm all right, yes. What about you?

911
01:29:00,092 --> 01:29:02,841
I just heard about Olivetti on the radio.
- I'm all right. I'm okay.

912
01:29:08,638 --> 01:29:10,779
Robert, we can't trust Richter.

913
01:29:10,783 --> 01:29:14,409
He took Silvano's journals.
There must be something in there
he doesn't want us to see.

914
01:29:14,420 --> 01:29:16,548
The head of the Swiss Guard.

915
01:29:17,963 --> 01:29:22,414
From the Castel Sant'Angelo. It's
close enough so the wireless signal
from that camera could still reach the Vatican.

916
01:29:24,166 --> 01:29:27,054
The Church of Illumination is somewhere here...

917
01:29:27,586 --> 01:29:29,602
and your canister is inside it.

918
01:29:49,364 --> 01:29:50,805
Come with me.

919
01:29:54,849 --> 01:29:58,020
For 400 years, the Illuminati met
right under the Church's nose.

920
01:29:58,025 --> 01:30:01,181
The Vatican used this as a
hideout and as a prison for their enemies.

921
01:30:01,802 --> 01:30:05,751
If the explosion happens here, would the
blast radius take out the Vatican?

922
01:30:05,923 --> 01:30:08,515
And part of Rome along with it.

923
01:30:25,860 --> 01:30:27,498
They're pointing to it. The angels.

924
01:30:27,582 --> 01:30:29,517
The container must be down there. Come on!

925
01:31:15,833 --> 01:31:18,935
Where are they going?
- Back to search the other castle.

926
01:31:19,585 --> 01:31:21,281
No, no. It has to be here!

927
01:31:25,185 --> 01:31:26,885
Robert, it's a dead end.

928
01:31:27,590 --> 01:31:28,822
No, it's not.

929
01:31:29,244 --> 01:31:31,346
See if you can find a flashlight.

930
01:31:47,987 --> 01:31:50,342
All of these stones are
rectangular granite.

931
01:31:50,524 --> 01:31:52,794
Except right here.
What is this?

932
01:31:57,030 --> 01:31:58,662
It's a pentagram.

933
01:31:58,823 --> 01:32:00,060
An eye...

934
01:32:00,611 --> 01:32:02,042
that leads to...

935
01:32:02,046 --> 01:32:03,202
Nowhere.

936
01:32:12,269 --> 01:32:13,269
Robert?

937
01:32:15,406 --> 01:32:18,474
These walls overlap
and there's a passageway in here.

938
01:32:18,542 --> 01:32:19,923
Here. Let me have the flashlight.

939
01:32:42,407 --> 01:32:45,449
It's a passageway that
leads to the Vatican.

940
01:32:45,484 --> 01:32:47,948
An ancient escape route.

941
01:32:50,231 --> 01:32:51,654
Oh, God.

942
01:32:53,563 --> 01:32:54,651
Here.

943
01:32:57,231 --> 01:32:58,451
Look.

944
01:33:30,451 --> 01:33:31,766
Get on the radio.

945
01:33:31,767 --> 01:33:34,669
Get the word out. Conclave remains sealed.

946
01:33:34,673 --> 01:33:36,632
The Camerlengo gave the
order for evacuation at...

947
01:33:36,793 --> 01:33:38,218
I'm countermanning it.

948
01:33:44,002 --> 01:33:45,991
This is it. This is their church.

949
01:33:48,318 --> 01:33:50,999
The canister should be
lit by artificial light.

950
01:34:14,343 --> 01:34:15,589
It's not here, Robert.

951
01:34:15,593 --> 01:34:17,961
"The shining star at the end of the path."
It has to be.

952
01:34:17,969 --> 01:34:19,720
It's not here.

953
01:34:19,902 --> 01:34:22,057
What did the poem say?
- Nothing.

954
01:34:22,108 --> 01:34:25,065
Nothing. It's all over.
There was just four lines...

955
01:34:25,157 --> 01:34:27,200
each one describing...

956
01:34:36,347 --> 01:34:38,172
There's a fifth brand.

957
01:34:38,268 --> 01:34:40,376
It's not an ambigram.
It's just two crossed keys.

958
01:34:40,377 --> 01:34:42,821
The symbol for the Vatican.
- No.

959
01:34:43,828 --> 01:34:47,013
No, the papacy.
They intend to kill him.

960
01:34:47,048 --> 01:34:49,297
Before they destroy the Vatican...

961
01:34:49,298 --> 01:34:52,195
they're going to brand and kill the
pope himself.
- There is no pope.

962
01:34:52,573 --> 01:34:54,329
"Tempo Sede Vacante."

963
01:34:54,364 --> 01:34:56,065
The Camerlengo.

964
01:34:57,705 --> 01:34:59,964
We have to warn him.
- Take a step back, please.

965
01:35:01,491 --> 01:35:03,713
Take your cell phone from your pocket.

966
01:35:06,863 --> 01:35:08,604
Throw it in the fire.

967
01:35:19,000 --> 01:35:20,825
Murderer.

968
01:35:20,860 --> 01:35:22,784
You know, when they call me...

969
01:35:23,434 --> 01:35:24,542
and they all call me...

970
01:35:24,577 --> 01:35:26,156
it is so important to them...

971
01:35:26,163 --> 01:35:29,709
that I know that what they ask
is the Lord's will.

972
01:35:29,714 --> 01:35:32,820
Or Allah's. Or Yahweh's.

973
01:35:33,700 --> 01:35:35,559
And I suppose they're right.

974
01:35:40,003 --> 01:35:44,044
Because if he was not vengeful,
I would not exist, now, would I?

975
01:35:44,080 --> 01:35:46,799
I've had several chances
to eliminate you tonight.

976
01:35:46,806 --> 01:35:50,674
You're still alive because you have no weapons.
And they didn't ask me to kill you.

977
01:35:50,679 --> 01:35:53,828
But if you pursue me,
it is another matter.

978
01:36:00,863 --> 01:36:02,078
Be careful.

979
01:36:02,646 --> 01:36:04,625
These are men of God.

980
01:36:16,687 --> 01:36:17,884
The Camerlengo.

981
01:36:26,306 --> 01:36:28,729
Have you come to make me a martyr?

982
01:36:36,948 --> 01:36:37,962
Here. Here.

983
01:38:01,333 --> 01:38:03,356
I need to see the Camerlengo.
- He is not available.

984
01:38:03,358 --> 01:38:05,890
I demand to see the Camerlengo.
- He is not available.

985
01:38:07,577 --> 01:38:08,959
We'll see about that.

986
01:38:18,207 --> 01:38:20,819
Oh. It's a chiusa chiave.
It's a one way portal.

987
01:38:20,859 --> 01:38:22,981
The only entrance is on the other side.

988
01:38:23,534 --> 01:38:25,651
No. Hey! Aiuto!

989
01:38:33,730 --> 01:38:36,129
This is Robert Langdon and Dr. Vetra.
Open the door.

990
01:38:49,006 --> 01:38:50,870
The Camerlengo is in danger.

991
01:39:04,058 --> 01:39:06,614
He's the one.
He's got a gun.

992
01:39:10,082 --> 01:39:12,304
Illuminatus.
- You bastard.

993
01:39:12,873 --> 01:39:13,451
Illuminatus!

994
01:39:13,707 --> 01:39:15,106
You bastard!

995
01:39:22,944 --> 01:39:23,909
Padre?

996
01:39:23,984 --> 01:39:27,437
Order the evacuation.
We only have nineteen minutes.

997
01:39:31,178 --> 01:39:32,808
Here. He's...

998
01:39:32,893 --> 01:39:35,612
And get the helicopter for
the older cardinals, right?
- Yes, sir.

999
01:39:49,113 --> 01:39:50,126
Robert?

1000
01:39:50,289 --> 01:39:53,048
The brand, the symbol.
Could it have another meaning?

1001
01:39:59,384 --> 01:40:02,582
Crossed keys, but
those were upside down.

1002
01:40:02,617 --> 01:40:04,182
St. Peter.

1003
01:40:05,070 --> 01:40:06,871
The first pope.

1004
01:40:07,974 --> 01:40:10,843
Was crucified upside down.
- On Vatican Hill.

1005
01:40:10,849 --> 01:40:13,712
A few hundred feet below us.
- Necropolis. City of the dead.

1006
01:40:13,714 --> 01:40:16,358
"Upon this rock, I will build my church."

1007
01:40:16,362 --> 01:40:18,888
"Or bring it down upon itself."

1008
01:40:19,664 --> 01:40:22,882
The bomb. It's in St. Peter's tomb.

1009
01:40:37,296 --> 01:40:38,835
The grid is still cycling.

1010
01:40:38,836 --> 01:40:40,741
The power to this section must be down.

1011
01:41:26,408 --> 01:41:29,212
It must be here. It must be.

1012
01:41:40,006 --> 01:41:41,177
Don't touch it.

1013
01:41:42,682 --> 01:41:44,232
We have seven minutes.

1014
01:41:50,142 --> 01:41:52,339
Robert, hold this.

1015
01:42:31,643 --> 01:42:34,093
It's cold down here, isn't it?

1016
01:42:34,097 --> 01:42:35,456
What's wrong?

1017
01:42:35,543 --> 01:42:38,079
Cold decreases battery life.

1018
01:42:40,077 --> 01:42:43,402
We may have less than five minutes.
- So?

1019
01:42:43,437 --> 01:42:46,334
If I pull the power with
less than five minutes...

1020
01:42:46,339 --> 01:42:49,270
the residual charge
won't hold suspension.

1021
01:42:50,385 --> 01:42:53,469
We should leave it here and get
clear if we can. At least down
here the damage...

1022
01:42:53,470 --> 01:42:54,802
No!

1023
01:42:56,265 --> 01:42:57,732
- No. Wait!
- Father!

1024
01:43:00,253 --> 01:43:02,286
We are live here at St. Peter's Square...

1025
01:43:02,290 --> 01:43:05,582
where, despite a bomb threat,
and an order of evacuation...

1026
01:43:05,589 --> 01:43:08,274
the crowd is actually growing in size.

1027
01:43:08,279 --> 01:43:11,075
As we wait an official announcement
from the Vatican spokesman...

1028
01:43:11,080 --> 01:43:13,165
as to the exact nature of the threat...

1029
01:43:13,169 --> 01:43:16,144
and whether or not they are
treating it as a credible danger.

1030
01:43:24,298 --> 01:43:25,202
This way!

1031
01:43:54,370 --> 01:43:55,583
He's got a bomb with him.

1032
01:43:56,821 --> 01:43:57,882
A bomb?

1033
01:44:03,147 --> 01:44:05,704
Roberto, this is an emergency.
I'll take her up alone.

1034
01:44:10,419 --> 01:44:12,469
He's got clearance.

1035
01:44:36,314 --> 01:44:38,876
Oh, my God.

1036
01:46:35,112 --> 01:46:36,753
Get down!

1037
01:49:22,028 --> 01:49:23,352
Cardinal Strauss?

1038
01:49:24,152 --> 01:49:27,727
It was the Camerlengo.
He has saved us all.

1039
01:49:28,320 --> 01:49:31,448
He has saved the Church
and he's still alive.

1040
01:49:32,806 --> 01:49:34,817
Praise God. Praise God.

1041
01:49:40,089 --> 01:49:41,330
He is alive.

1042
01:49:41,842 --> 01:49:44,578
He sacrificed himself for all of us.

1043
01:50:11,766 --> 01:50:14,541
You know the worst thing we
thought would happen?

1044
01:50:15,717 --> 01:50:19,031
Was that our work would fall
into the hands of the energy companies.

1045
01:50:21,773 --> 01:50:23,500
We thought we could change the world.

1046
01:50:24,378 --> 01:50:28,164
So naive.
- No, not naive.

1047
01:50:29,274 --> 01:50:30,745
Innocent, maybe.

1048
01:50:31,314 --> 01:50:33,452
But it's not a crime.

1049
01:50:34,902 --> 01:50:36,290
I'm not so sure.

1050
01:50:38,348 --> 01:50:40,106
Go back to work.

1051
01:50:41,301 --> 01:50:42,885
Change the world.

1052
01:51:02,979 --> 01:51:08,582
A gift, uh, you understand?
Let's say for Catholics everywhere.

1053
01:51:08,795 --> 01:51:11,455
The Carmelengo's age shouldn't reach
the decision.

1054
01:51:11,634 --> 01:51:17,204
Signori, you are no doubt aware
that the Holy Law of that man is
inelligible for election to the papacy.

1055
01:51:17,540 --> 01:51:20,797
He's not a cardinal. He's a priest.
He's of insufficient age.

1056
01:51:21,007 --> 01:51:23,878
Or maybe there's a way we
could consider the possibility.

1057
01:51:24,071 --> 01:51:28,039
I am sorry. The protocols of conclave
are not subject to modification.

1058
01:51:28,208 --> 01:51:31,026
I will not call a
ballot on this matter.

1059
01:51:31,232 --> 01:51:33,808
But, signore, you would not hold a ballot.

1060
01:51:34,011 --> 01:51:37,384
Surely, you remember? You gave
up your post as Great Elector.

1061
01:51:38,121 --> 01:51:40,264
They are singing at St. Peter's Square.

1062
01:51:40,452 --> 01:51:43,088
Now, what happened here tonight
transcends our laws.

1063
01:51:43,308 --> 01:51:48,044
Has it? Is it God's will that we
give ourselves over to frenzy?

1064
01:51:48,048 --> 01:51:49,479
Discard the rules of the Church?

1065
01:51:49,519 --> 01:51:51,719
Perhaps we need not discard them.

1066
01:51:52,345 --> 01:51:57,947
Signori, I am thinking now of
Romano Pontifici Eligendo numero 60...

1067
01:51:58,187 --> 01:52:01,081
Acclamation by Adoration.
- Exactly, signore. Exactly.

1068
01:52:01,350 --> 01:52:03,805
Yes. If the Holy Spirit speaks through us...

1069
01:52:04,326 --> 01:52:06,226
and we call a man's name out loud...

1070
01:52:06,420 --> 01:52:09,172
That is election by adoration.

1071
01:52:09,602 --> 01:52:11,429
He's God's choice.

1072
01:52:11,709 --> 01:52:17,448
Yes. And the candidate need only be an
ordained member of the clergy...

1073
01:52:17,452 --> 01:52:21,538
present in the Sistine Chapel
at the moment of his election.

1074
01:52:53,280 --> 01:52:54,325
Signor Camerlengo?

1075
01:52:55,258 --> 01:52:59,057
- Yes?
The cardinals ask you to join
them in conclave as soon as possible.

1076
01:52:59,142 --> 01:53:01,634
Me?
- Yes, Padre.

1077
01:53:24,425 --> 01:53:25,981
What are you doing?

1078
01:53:26,063 --> 01:53:28,542
Silvano's journals. I want them back.

1079
01:53:52,272 --> 01:53:53,745
Richter said...

1080
01:53:55,566 --> 01:53:57,900
His Holiness suffered from seizures...

1081
01:53:57,905 --> 01:54:00,412
and steps were taken...

1082
01:54:00,621 --> 01:54:02,519
for safety.

1083
01:54:06,524 --> 01:54:09,069
He made sure he was watched he said.

1084
01:54:11,152 --> 01:54:14,095
What if he were trying
to give me this key?

1085
01:54:15,259 --> 01:54:17,226
That's the Papal office.

1086
01:54:17,660 --> 01:54:22,486
If the Pope was worried about
seizures, he must've had Richter
install cameras without telling anyone.

1087
01:54:22,521 --> 01:54:25,323
To keep an eye on him for his safety.

1088
01:54:26,786 --> 01:54:28,761
Maybe it records.

1089
01:54:39,127 --> 01:54:43,772
I read the journals, Patrick.
- The scientist kept journals. So?

1090
01:54:43,773 --> 01:54:47,139
You figure prominently in them.
- Really?

1091
01:54:47,141 --> 01:54:51,741
The Devoli wasn't just a physicist.
He was also a Catholic priest.

1092
01:54:52,439 --> 01:54:58,626
As such, he was deeply conflicted
about the implications of his work
and in need of spiritual guidance.

1093
01:54:58,634 --> 01:55:00,398
Like Galileo.

1094
01:55:01,239 --> 01:55:03,045
About a month ago...

1095
01:55:03,049 --> 01:55:06,313
he requested an audience with the Pope.
But you know that.

1096
01:55:06,505 --> 01:55:09,786
You soon granted the audience and
you were also present during it.

1097
01:55:09,788 --> 01:55:12,966
The 'God Particle'.
To actually claim an act of creation.

1098
01:55:12,967 --> 01:55:17,354
The blasphemy. The arrogance.
- The Holy Father didn't see it like that.

1099
01:55:17,459 --> 01:55:19,559
He urged him to go public.

1100
01:55:19,564 --> 01:55:25,608
His Holiness thought that the discovery
could actually scientifically prove the
existence of a divine power.

1101
01:55:25,611 --> 01:55:28,814
And begin to bridge the gap between
science and religion.

1102
01:55:28,818 --> 01:55:31,420
His work was not religious.
It was sacrilegious.

1103
01:55:31,422 --> 01:55:32,234
But you...

1104
01:55:33,124 --> 01:55:36,864
You saw the pope's position as
a softening of church law.

1105
01:55:36,869 --> 01:55:40,684
As an old man's weakness.
Your father's weakness.

1106
01:55:40,719 --> 01:55:44,537
You murdered the Vicar of Christ.
- He raised me to protect this Church...

1107
01:55:44,540 --> 01:55:46,123
even from within.

1108
01:55:47,867 --> 01:55:52,450
Then you conjured up an old
enemy from the past. The Illuminati.

1109
01:55:52,485 --> 01:55:56,007
You found the ancient brands in
the papal vaults and put them to use...

1110
01:55:56,729 --> 01:55:59,992
to spread fear!
- The Cardinals are men of belief.

1111
01:56:00,029 --> 01:56:04,015
Right now, their belief in evil
is uniting them.

1112
01:56:04,020 --> 01:56:07,015
The entire Catholic world will
be united by this attack.

1113
01:56:07,020 --> 01:56:08,602
There is no attack.

1114
01:56:09,562 --> 01:56:12,788
You're trying to convince the
Cardinals they're in a war...

1115
01:56:12,793 --> 01:56:14,638
so they will choose a warrior
to lead them.

1116
01:56:14,642 --> 01:56:16,076
We are at war.

1117
01:56:16,078 --> 01:56:18,115
We're weak when we should be strong.

1118
01:56:18,119 --> 01:56:22,014
If science is allowed to claim
the power of creation...

1119
01:56:22,028 --> 01:56:23,786
what is left for God?

1120
01:56:23,821 --> 01:56:25,745
It didn't work, Patrick.

1121
01:56:26,633 --> 01:56:29,619
It isn't finished.
- Oh, yes, it's finished.

1122
01:56:31,691 --> 01:56:33,082
It's finished.

1123
01:56:33,940 --> 01:56:37,145
I've shown the journals to
Father Simeon.

1124
01:56:37,151 --> 01:56:39,331
The moment the doors
to the Conclave open...

1125
01:56:39,337 --> 01:56:41,492
he will tell the Cardinals
what you've done.

1126
01:56:42,381 --> 01:56:44,591
I was planning on doing this alone.

1127
01:56:47,866 --> 01:56:49,050
Put it down.

1128
01:56:52,065 --> 01:56:54,092
But, perhaps, it's better
that you're here.

1129
01:56:54,139 --> 01:56:55,520
Put it down.

1130
01:56:57,419 --> 01:56:59,156
Put it away.

1131
01:57:10,224 --> 01:57:13,820
Help. He's the one.
He's got a gun.

1132
01:57:17,464 --> 01:57:19,896
Illuminatus.
- You bastard.

1133
01:57:20,253 --> 01:57:21,015
Illuminatus!

1134
01:57:21,021 --> 01:57:22,167
You bastard!

1135
01:57:26,246 --> 01:57:27,353
Padre.

1136
01:57:37,255 --> 01:57:40,423
And get the helicopter for
the older cardinals, right?

1137
01:58:29,871 --> 01:58:32,414
I've been summoned
by the College of Cardinals.

1138
01:59:42,437 --> 01:59:43,756
Gently.

1139
01:59:44,064 --> 01:59:45,438
But within our walls.

1140
01:59:57,560 --> 02:00:00,023
He's on your side.

1141
02:00:46,353 --> 02:00:50,261
Father, into thy hands I commend my spirit.

1142
02:01:38,160 --> 02:01:46,800
Church sources now confirm that Carmelengo,
Father Patrick McKenna, has died of internal
injuries sustained in his heroic fall...

1143
02:01:48,120 --> 02:01:54,560
The Catholic church thanks Camerlengo
for his selfless act and demands his immediate canonization.

1144
02:01:54,640 --> 02:01:59,651
The Vatican has also confirmed the
deaths of three Cardinals and the fire
in the Santa Maria della Vittoria.

1145
02:01:59,746 --> 02:02:04,021
As we await the appearance of
the new Holy Father Cardinal
Baggia of Italy...

1146
02:02:04,150 --> 02:02:05,725
one of the four original Preferiti...

1147
02:02:06,233 --> 02:02:08,374
who, despite terrorist
attempts at disruption...

1148
02:02:08,414 --> 02:02:14,022
seems to have been selected in one of
the swiftest and smoothest conclaves
in modern church history.

1149
02:02:21,116 --> 02:02:22,869
Professor Langdon?
Please.

1150
02:02:38,603 --> 02:02:42,059
A token of thanks from
His Holiness...

1151
02:02:42,561 --> 02:02:44,799
and from his new Camerlengo.

1152
02:02:46,273 --> 02:02:49,028
We are grateful you saved his life.

1153
02:02:49,137 --> 02:02:52,665
And it's our understanding that you
require this text...

1154
02:02:52,670 --> 02:02:55,165
to complete your scholary work.

1155
02:02:56,397 --> 02:03:01,198
We ask only that in your
last grand testament...

1156
02:03:01,267 --> 02:03:04,061
you ensure it finds its way home.

1157
02:03:06,474 --> 02:03:07,823
Of course.

1158
02:03:08,041 --> 02:03:10,011
And when you write of us...

1159
02:03:10,134 --> 02:03:12,783
and you will write of us...

1160
02:03:13,032 --> 02:03:14,976
may I ask one thing?

1161
02:03:15,473 --> 02:03:17,196
Do so gently.

1162
02:03:18,948 --> 02:03:20,385
I'll try.

1163
02:03:20,981 --> 02:03:22,685
Religion is flawed...

1164
02:03:23,358 --> 02:03:26,263
but only because man is flawed.

1165
02:03:26,267 --> 02:03:28,881
All men,
including this one.

1166
02:03:43,425 --> 02:03:45,377
He chose the name Luke.

1167
02:03:47,987 --> 02:03:51,062
There's been many Marks and Johns.

1168
02:03:52,167 --> 02:03:54,043
Never a Luke.

1169
02:03:54,408 --> 02:03:56,537
It said he was a doctor.

1170
02:03:56,981 --> 02:04:00,501
It's quite a message.
Science and faith, all in one.

1171
02:04:01,406 --> 02:04:03,473
The world is in need of both.

1172
02:04:05,183 --> 02:04:07,326
You'll counsel him wisely.

1173
02:04:08,181 --> 02:04:10,974
I'm an old man.
I'll counsel him briefly.

1174
02:04:16,800 --> 02:04:18,666
Mr. Langdon.

1175
02:04:23,689 --> 02:04:28,410
Thanks be to God for sending someone
to protect this church.

1176
02:04:32,341 --> 02:04:35,683
I don't believe He sent me, Father.

1177
02:04:35,744 --> 02:04:37,304
Oh, my son.

1178
02:04:37,766 --> 02:04:39,685
Of course He did.


